{"tid":1192673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六檔案經典一集在71後（2003年）","createTime":"2019-06-08T14:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T14:22:09.000Z","uid":157522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b776a74abeb21a5bf300fe234e65f75835e375","tid":1192673,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y1iz_LpT4Zc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY1iz_LpT4Zc&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=893e9df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y1iz_LpT4Zc</a><br />\n港區全國人大代表鄔維庸指，不應<span style=\"color: red;\">以為人多、壓力升級就幻想可以不立法</span>，政府可讓步的都讓了，現在<span style=\"color: red;\">要讓步的應是市民</span>。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日，晚上行政長官董建華發表書面聲明，關注很多市民參與遊行，理解他們所表達的訴求。他並謂，特區政府充分了解市民重視人權和自由，政府的立場和市民一致。其後兩天他在上班時僅以「早晨（早安）」二字回應記者各種提問。民建聯的陳鑑林及曾鈺成先後於訪問中指遊行人士是被「誤導」，當中<span style=\"color: red;\">陳鑑林</span>是在鄰近維園的天后地鐵站內接受無綫電視記者訪問時，指「他們（即遊行者）都是被誤導的」，即時被正前往遊行的群眾喝倒采，這個片段在當日不斷重覆播放。兩人事後均道歉。<br />\n<br />\n7月9日，民間人權陣線在立法會附近集會，董建華表示會抱持開放態度。最後主辦單位公布有5萬人參加集會，會後有市民向政府官員及在23條立法問題上支持政府的議員座駕喝倒采，亦有市民擲熒光棒。立法會議員<span style=\"color: red;\">黃宜弘</span>在乘車離開時，笑著向在場市民舉中指（不雅手勢，等同向在場市民講粗言穢語），過程被電視台及記者攝下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20030710/Article_news/10la8p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20030710%2FArticle_news%2F10la8p4.jpg&h=2cba9045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月16日，保安局局長<span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉淑儀</span>與財政司司長<span style=\"color: red;\">梁錦松</span>於晚上先後在七時多及九時多<span style=\"color: red;\">公布辭職</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">事後</span>葉劉淑儀出席香港工聯會致敬晚會，致辭時說看到社會有時有「歪風」、有人「顛倒是非，黑白不分」。<br />\n<br />\n9月5日，董建華<span style=\"color: red;\">宣布撤回《國家安全（立法條文）條例草案》</span>，承諾先搞好經濟，並會再次充份諮詢市民，達到共識後才再立法，重申沒有立法時間表。<br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2003%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C#%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2003%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%23%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=38a15a64\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2003%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C#%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2003年都得，2019年無理由唔得嘅!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca731f9a75efeacf030f3b997d9d6bd6b24e1c0","tid":1192673,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 我唔後入你已經讓左步 快撚啲讓步比個閪我入啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9411ed3dbc6223709f0f6934cb4424b2a7c017d","tid":1192673,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"Assemble!!!"}]}